      <title>SAP、Carahsoft 调查范围扩大至近 100 家机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/sap-carahsoft-probe-expanded-to-work-with-nearly-100-agencies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据新的法庭记录，美国检察官正在扩大对德国软件制造商 SAP SE 和技术经销商 Carahsoft Technology Corp. 可能存在的价格操纵的调查，试图调查这两家公司与近 100 个政府机构的合作情况，调查范围远远超出之前所知。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/sap-carahsoft-probe-expanded-to-work-with-nearly-100-agencies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 21:43:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飓风导致矿场关闭，芯片公司关注石英供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/chip-firms-monitoring-quartz-supplies-after-hurricane-hits-mines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风海伦 (Hurricane Helene) 导致北卡罗来纳州两座矿山停产，这两座矿山生产的石英占全球石英产量的绝大部分。此后，全球半导体制造商都在监控高纯度石英（一种对半导体行业至关重要的材料）的供应情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/chip-firms-monitoring-quartz-supplies-after-hurricane-hits-mines</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
